name: CELESTIAL SENTINELS: Talk Time x Props

metadata.name: CELESTIAL SENTINEL #1
metadata.description:
As our two astronauts flee an exploding gas planet in their escape pod, they are greeted by a celestial guardian who sucks them into a stargate portal.

The duo is hurled beyond time and space, and their seemingly disastrous mission is redeemed when they find themselves at their mission objective; an audience with THE supreme being.

CELESTIAL SENTINELS is a collection of unique pieces of art, representing what you might experience as you are greeted by the guardian and ride through the portal, each teleportation varying based on your lived experiences.

Inspired by the epic frame-by-frame animated music video for NECESSARY EVIL:
https://youtube.com/watch?v=mOQJKsCi4Ag 

More info at https://talktimeband.com
